Change-Id: I6600f834b031b6c832176f640b0b481d6af8a371

Verify "get version" API response attributes

Now most attributes of Nova v2/v3 APIs are not checked in Tempest,
and this patch adds some tests which check these attributes to block
the backward incompatibility change in the future.

This patch adds the checks of "get version" API responses.
The response body of this API is the following:

{
    "version":{
        'id': 'v3.0',
        'links': [
            {
                'href': 'http://127.0.0.1:8774/v3/'
                'rel': 'self'
            },
            {
                'href': 'http://docs.openstack.org/api/...'
                'rel': 'describedby'
                'type': 'application/pdf'
            },
            {
                'href': 'http://docs.openstack.org/api/...'
                'rel': 'describedby'
                'type': 'application/vnd.sun.wadl+xml'
            },
        ],
        'media-types': [
            {
                'base': 'application/json'
                'type': 'application/vnd.openstack.compute+...'
            },
        },
        'status': 'EXPERIMENTAL',
        'updated': '2013-07-23T11:33:21Z',
    }
}

Partially implements blueprint nova-api-attribute-test

